data.description: Remodeled, well cared for 4 bedroom, 2 full bath, laminate wood floors, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash in kitchen. On-suite has a walk in closet. The 4th bedroom is more usable as an office, but does have a closet. Laundry in garage. Ductless heat pump. Large backyard with plenty of space for entertaining, covered front porch, close to park and schools. Great location, super cute home!
